name: box collection green
description: Here are 10 more boxes  out of the 150 total.  This is the box collection green colour edition 8/10 colour (with a rarity of medium). With a starting price of 2 tez, but the bonding curve is different (to box collection red) and will not be shared. The link attached here ( box collection) is the white paper to the box collection plan and more information about Different boxes that can be found and obtained. With the rarity scheme and general knowledge. Green really inspires me and takes me back to the first, i love this piece and i hope so do you. What it means to me if you Purchas parts of the box collection: You will give me a green light/incentive to do more art. You will motivate and support a young artist who is trying to understand the world and ground his feet. It will make him feel valued and reassure that making art day after day is the right thing to do. If you cannot support me buy purchasing a piece of box collection, you can drop a comment and/or a like on my socials. Let's connect further, here is my link tree(https://linktr.ee/energetic_pen)
